# Code Style Rules

## TypeScript
- Use strict TypeScript configuration for all [*.ts](mdc:src) files.
- Define interfaces for all props in [*.tsx](mdc:src) files.
- Avoid using the `any` type in [*.ts](mdc:src) files.

## React
- Use functional components in all [*.tsx](mdc:src) files.
- Implement proper prop types in all [*.tsx](mdc:src) files.

## Styling
- Use Tailwind CSS classes in [*.tsx](mdc:src) files.
- Follow shadcn/ui component patterns in [*.tsx](mdc:src) files.

## Development Workflow
- Commit automatically after each code change that has been tested and all tests pass.
